{"tid":1181000,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"移交條例取代方法","createTime":"2019-06-01T09:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T07:05:47.000Z","uid":241224,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"609d78760de62b598859e2383c2a5bb750d50f46","tid":1181000,"uid":241224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T09:15:04.000Z","msg":"該國政府以檢察官(律政司)身份既方式來港作起訴<br />\n用佢地既條例黎起訴個犯(殺人罪行條例)<br />\n但用香港既原則 (presumption of innocence)個d<br />\n黎判d逃犯<br />\n再追加個條<br />\n如果辯方可以證明自己有政治背景(政治犯)就<br />\n可以免判(基於證據偽造)，或者喺香港判監(人身安全)"},{"pid":"09da7a08f49e6f9c85888bf236bc0386f30830dc","tid":1181000,"uid":241224,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T09:18:49.000Z","msg":"如果有取代方案，咁就可以唔洗好似咁移交"},{"pid":"4ae29250566990c7acb00373bb5943e18a6ce6f5","tid":1181000,"uid":241224,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T09:20:46.000Z","msg":"唔好留低負評就走，想理性討論"},{"pid":"ab322be8e95289e0f854aa776e7885d797035ee3","tid":1181000,"uid":241224,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T09:25:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f127e73f0b4e9fe26cfc74bd017fddef50a2a094","tid":1181000,"uid":3480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T09:26:28.000Z","msg":"用下你個閪腦諗下可唔可行"},{"pid":"ad7d5e66138bd5bf23058c2c58c0bd0e9ad2689a","tid":1181000,"uid":241224,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"f127e73f0b4e9fe26cfc74bd017fddef50a2a094","tid":1181000,"uid":3480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T09:26:28.000Z","msg":"用下你個閪腦諗下可唔可行"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T09:28:22.000Z","msg":"可唔可行係講緊個程序可唔可行<br />\n定其他國家畀唔畀香港小城市審可唔可行"},{"pid":"6aeff9ee75a4632a89ff72cf0f9727ca38ad379f","tid":1181000,"uid":241224,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T09:33:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79cd932b14e080a16fa7f17e0b5fdba4fbf8cb27","tid":1181000,"uid":241224,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T09:39:45.000Z",